some good arguements, some bad ones. anyone who says this war isnt partially about money/oil is an idiot. BUT anyone who says this war is ONLY about oil/money is a bigger idiot.  would we be fighting it if it was in certain south american or central american countries (were dictators more ruthless than saddam have killed many more than saddam in teh last 10 years).. ? probably not.<br>
