did george W make his case tieing in terrorism to saddam?  didnt convince me. <br>
<br>
BUT....<br>
<br>
keep in mind several things. 12 years ago, when i WAS in the desert, we let saddam go. we made promises to the Iraqi people that if they rose up and fought saddam, 'uncle sam' would back them. did we? no. we allowed saddam to murder and oppress those people who fought for freedom, in the name of global peace, and cowing to the U.N.. <br>
<br>
