The pictures of soldiers and the list.... those were emotional arguments. But, I don't need pictures or lists to know that people are dieing. I don't see that people dieing justifies war.... To me it is an argument for peace.<br>
<br>
All of these men knew they could die, all of these men knew they were suposed to kill. That is just horible. No learned philosofy, no oath and no good intentions can justify this.<br>
<br>
Only one thing can.... to me a man can kill when he or his dear ones are in imediate danger. The danger was not to America. <br>
<br>
This could have been resolved without a war. If the world had tried to resolve the problem instead of placing blame. Now people have died. American soldiers, Iraqi soldiers and iraqi civilians.<br>
<br>
Yes, Saddam have comitted terible crimes. So put him on trial like any other criminal. If the situation had been resolved peacefully, the iraqi could do what chile never did..... they could put the dictator on trial  and convict him. Now they are deprived this libaration. <br>
<br>
I do not defend Sadam, I do not defend his regime. What I do defend is a nations right to look for a more peacefull solution. France have a right to decline a war. France is not a coward because of this. If anything, it took some courage to stand against America in this matter. <br>
<br>
I also defend the right of the iraqi people to find their own solution. They have not been given this option. Please, if you tell me that the iraqi is pro this war... also tell me when they voted... The fact is that you are equaly ignorant to me in these afairs... I can not be sure that the statistics don't lie.<br>
<br>
Ohh you are right, I never did join the armed forces. I saw no need to. I am not quite sure I could kill for my country. I do know that I could die for my country, that one is easy, but to kill...<br>
<br>
I will at any time fight for my country, but I pick the weapons. My weapon of choise is not a gun,  my weapon of choice is non cooperation, civil disobediance and even sabotage. <br>
<br>
So if you find your self occupying my country, you will find getting the people you don't like out of harms way, you will find me refusing to work for you and you will find me sabotaging your means of transport, your means of comunication and any respect for your reign that you try to built.<br>
<br>
